  "body": "From my understanding of the storage requirements for policing the network it should be \r\n54000 * 300000 * 328 bytes per attestation ~5.4 Tb \r\n54000 * 2344 committees per epoch * 328 bytes ~ 41gb using aggregated attestations\r\n8 months of proposals and validation data\r\n\r\nif those are the requirements I guess we at Prysmatic labs will go with this design https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1MkLraDsZJCX3k62bBtt8ziUdw308U2bW_w0lUmV-0YQ/edit?usp=sharing",
